<TITLE> Police arrest top criminal </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Madaripur, May 5 (bdnews24.com)The police arrested a top criminal at Shibchar upazila in Madaripur on Tuesday night. The arrested Liton Moral, 28, son of Sattar Moral, hails from Moralkandi village under Nikli union. Md Abdullah, OC of the Shibchar Police Station, told bdnews24.com that they had arrested Liton from a tea stall of Kala Mridha Bazar at around 10pm. Liton has five cases against him for murder, robbery, abduction and the possession of arms with Shibchar, Bhanga and Keraniganj Police Stations, the police officer said. bd
